{
  "texts": [
    "For example, COT_zs increases the accuracy on MCQ-M by 100%, 600%, and 133% in the three subjects.",
    "As there exist more than one correct options in MCQ-M questions which are much more complicated than MCQ-S ones, the above results confirm the effectiveness of COT in boosting the reasoning ability of LLMs.",
    "The above benchmarking results illustrate the large potential of LLMs in urban planning.",
    "In practical urban planning scenarios, LLMs can be smoothly integrated into planners' workflow using appropriate prompts, and we provide two example cases of urban planning text polishment and proofreading in Appendix A.",
    "Fine-tuning LLMs with UrbanPlanTextThe inherent knowledge of LLMs proves insufficient when confronted with specialized urban planning queries, highlighting a deficiency in domain-specific understanding."
  ]
}